tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE rental_prices (
  neighborhood VARCHAR(255),
  year INT,
  month INT,
  average_price DECIMAL(10, 2)
)

CREATE TABLE growth_patterns (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  neighborhood_id INT,
  growth_rate DECIMAL,
  trend_analysis TEXT,
  trend_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE rental_properties (
    property_id INT,
    neighborhood_id INT,
    property_type VARCHAR(100),
    num_bedrooms INT,
    num_bathrooms INT,
    square_feet INT
);

CREATE TABLE rental_properties (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  neighborhood VARCHAR(255),
  property_type VARCHAR(255),
  monthly_rent DECIMAL,
  year_built INT
)

CREATE TABLE rental_history (
  rental_id INT,
  rental_date DATE,
  rental_price DECIMAL,
  neighborhood VARCHAR(255),
  FOREIGN KEY (rental_id) REFERENCES rental_properties(id)
)

CREATE TABLE neighborhood_growth (
  neighborhood VARCHAR(255),
  growth_percentage DECIMAL,
  year INT
)

CREATE TABLE property_types (
  property_type VARCHAR(255),
  average_rent DECIMAL,
  total_properties INT
)

CREATE TABLE renter_profiles (
  renter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  gender VARCHAR(255),
  age INT,
  occupation VARCHAR(255),
  neighborhood_preference VARCHAR(255)
)
